Phase 2: Research Atom Pipeline + Usage Tracker\
Overview\
Build the research atom extraction pipeline (build_research_atoms.py) and usage tracker (research_atom_usage_tracker.py + JSON state). This makes research safe, traceable, and enforceable.\
\
Follows the CharacterUsageTracker pattern from tools/character_usage_tracker.py: JSON state file, can_use() / record_usage() methods, per-topic and per-entity limits.\
\
Phase 1 (validator) already enforces research placement, expiration, and section limits. Phase 2 adds the supply side: how atoms get created, how their usage gets tracked, and how quote exhaustion gets enforced.\
