Design choice: This is a structured template generator + validator, NOT an LLM auto-extractor. The dev spec says atoms are "extracted offline" \'97 the tool creates properly-structured templates from source files, validates them, and writes them. Human review fills in claims/quotes. This keeps atoms deterministic and writer-controlled.\
